ENTRY            F0522   20251214   20260305   20260305       F105
SUBENT        F0522001   20251214   20260305   20260305       F105
BIB                  9         16
TITLE      Structure studies of Na-23 from the 20Ne(alpha,p)23Na
           reaction at Ealpha=39.5 MeV
AUTHOR     (C.R.Bingham,K.Van Der Borg, R.J.De Meijer,
           A.Van Der Woude)
REFERENCE  (J,NP/A,323,26,1979)
INSTITUTE  (2NEDKVI,1USATEN)
FACILITY   (CYCLO,2NEDKVI) KVI cyclotron
SAMPLE     The target consists of a gas cell of 7.0 cm diam.
           with 1.8 mg/cm2 Kapton entrance and exit windows. The
           gas cell was filled with enriched 20Ne to a pressure
           of 200-300 Torr.
DETECTOR   (TELES,SI) Delta E-E counter telescope with a total Si
           detector depth of 7 mm.
METHOD     (EDE,BCINT)
HISTORY    (20030604C)
           (20251214A) SD: Corrections in all Subents.
ENDBIB              16
COMMON               2          3
EN         EN-RSL
MEV        KEV
 39.5       100.
ENDCOMMON            3
ENDSUBENT           23
