FLAG       (1.) Values uncertain due to incomplete angular
           distribution.
STATUS     (TABLE,,C.R.Bingham+,J,NP/A,323,26,1979) Table 1
HISTORY    (20251214A) SD: BIB updated. SF6=IPA -> DA;
           SF8=REL -> MSC in REACTION code.
